      answer: "Yes. Sharjah has several free zones including SAIF Zone, Sharjah Media City, and Sharjah Publishing City. We translate free zone documentation for banking, licensing, and other purposes."
    },
    {
      question: "Do you deliver to all Sharjah areas?",
      answer: "Yes. We deliver to all Sharjah locations including Al Nahda, Al Khan, Al Majaz, Al Qasimia, Industrial Areas, and surrounding communities. Delivery times are consistent across the emirate."
